class=\"card mb-2\"><div class=\"card-header\" id=\"heading4\"><h5 class=\"mb-0\"><button class=\"btn btn-link text-left collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#collapse4\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\"><i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>Collection Delays & Missing Annexures</button></h5></div> <div id=\"collapse4\" class=\"collapse\"><div class=\"card-body\"><p>Missing documents lead to delays in receiving the final registered copy.</p><p><strong>How to fix:</strong></p><ul><li>Ensure all IDs, photos, and annexures are attached. Track the document status online and collect it personally.</li></ul></div></div></div> <div class=\"card mb-2\"><div class=\"card-header\" id=\"heading5\"><h5 class=\"mb-0\"><button class=\"btn btn-link text-left collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#collapse5\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\"><i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>Witness Verification Issues</button></h5></div> <div id=\"collapse5\" class=\"collapse\"><div class=\"card-body\"><p>If witnesses turn hostile or pass away, proving the Will is difficult.</p><p><strong>How to fix:</strong></p><ul><li>Select younger, trustworthy witnesses. Consider executing a new Will if key witnesses pass away.</li></ul></div></div></div></div>"
